    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been consistently maintained to ensure reliable performance. The engine runs strong, the transmission shifts smoothly, and all major mechanical systems are in solid working order. While there are some minor cosmetic signs of use consistent with its age, the interior remains clean and comfortable. This is a dependable car that is ready for daily use without any immediate need for repairs.",
