    },
    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Looking for a rewarding project or a budget-friendly way to get on the road? This car is ready for someone with a vision! While it currently requires some significant mechanical and cosmetic attention, it serves as a fantastic foundation for a restoration enthusiast or anyone looking for a valuable source of parts. It's an honest vehicle with a lot of potential for the right hands!",
