    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presenting an automotive specimen of uncompromising caliber. This vehicle is maintained in pristine, showroom condition, representing the pinnacle of its class. Every surface, from the flawless exterior finish to the immaculate interior upholstery, reflects a standard of care that is rarely encountered in the pre-owned market. Mechanically peerless and aesthetically perfect, this offering is suited for the discerning collector who demands excellence without exception. We invite you to experience a level of refinement that defines the upper echelon of automotive preservation.",
      "price": 46500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 10
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m selling my absolute pride and joy, and let me tell you, she is a total stunner! This car has been pampered like a member of the family\u2014always garage-kept, meticulously detailed, and it still has that fresh, new-car feel. It's in truly pristine condition inside and out, with not a single scratch or smudge to be found. It drives like an absolute dream! I'm looking for a buyer who will appreciate just how well-maintained this beauty is. Come take a look, you won't be disappointed!",
      "price": 44500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 10
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This 1994 Mazda RX-7 FD is a museum-grade example of the front-midship, rear-drive icon. The 13B-REW sequential twin-turbocharged rotary engine is in peak mechanical condition, exhibiting stellar compression across all rotor faces. The complex vacuum-actuated turbo transition remains crisp and linear, while the five-speed manual gearbox offers precise gate entry with no synchro wear. The chassis retains its factory-spec four-wheel double-wishbone suspension and Torsen limited-slip differential, providing the telepathic handling and 50:50 weight distribution that defined the FD. This is an unmolested, collector-quality specimen with original paint and a pristine interior, free from the typical heat-cycling degradation found in lesser examples.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 10
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Used car. Mint condition. Garage kept. No accidents. Clean title. Service records available. Ready for inspection.",
      "price": 44500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 10
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Offered here is a truly exceptional example that has been meticulously preserved in a climate-controlled garage since new. The exterior paint is entirely original and possesses a deep, mirror-like finish, free from any rock chips, swirls, or imperfections. Inside, the cabin remains in showroom condition; the leather seats show no signs of bolster wear, and every electronic component\u2014from the infotainment system to the seat heaters\u2014functions flawlessly. Mechanically, the vehicle is in peak form, supported by a comprehensive binder of every service record performed at authorized intervals. There are no leaks, no odd noises, and the undercarriage is as clean as the bodywork. This car is a time capsule, offering a driving experience indistinguishable from the day it left the dealership. I welcome any independent pre-purchase inspection to confirm its pristine status.",
      "price": 44500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 10
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "Presenting a peerless example of automotive excellence. This vehicle is offered in impeccable, showroom-grade condition, having undergone a rigorous multi-point inspection to ensure it meets the most exacting standards of performance and aesthetics. The exterior finish remains flawless, complemented by an interior that retains its original factory luster. For the collector or enthusiast who demands nothing short of perfection, this offering represents a rare opportunity to acquire a truly pristine specimen. We invite serious inquiries to experience this masterclass in engineering firsthand.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 10
